&lt;p&gt;The world of digital retail media, music, and television is in the midst of explosive growth as brick-and-mortar businesses seek to create savvy, personalized, and engaging experiences for their customers, patrons, and members.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And Rockbot wants the same.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking an agency-grade Director of Brand and Creative Services who sets—and defends—an uncompromising standard of excellence and innovation for our brand. As our creative leader, you will help us re-express a well-defined and articulated brand identity that is evolving rapidly as we grow, scale and innovate. This role requires a rare blend of visionary thinking and hands-on craft: someone who can architect a creative direction that stands up to scrutiny, then jump into the work to ensure every detail meets the highest bar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting directly to the SVP of Marketing, you’ll be responsible for delivering top-grade visual storytelling that elevates and energizes our brand, deepens market differentiation, and resonates through every channel—from major campaigns to the smallest design element. If you thrive on creating standout work, reimagining brands as they grow, and fiercely protecting creative integrity, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a true player-coach role that blends creative vision, brand stewardship, team leadership, and hands-on craft. Your time will be thoughtfully balanced across:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20% Creative Direction &amp;amp; Brand Evolution&lt;/strong&gt;: shaping the future of the Rockbot brand and setting the creative standard across the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20% Hands-On Creative Execution&lt;/strong&gt;: rolling up your sleeves to bring ideas to life and elevate key deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20% Team Leadership &amp;amp; Creative Mentorship&lt;/strong&gt;: inspiring, developing, and raising the bar for creative talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20% Campaign Development &amp;amp; Visual Storytelling&lt;/strong&gt;: conceiving and delivering memorable, high-impact brand moments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10% Creative Operations &amp;amp; Systems&lt;/strong&gt;: building scalable processes that enable exceptional work at speed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10% Agency &amp;amp; External Partner Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;: directing and managing creative partners to ensure excellence and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a creative leader who is equally energized by defining the vision, developing great talent, and personally shaping the work that brings a brand to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have the freedom (and responsibility) to accelerate a brand that is in a transformation stage, and have the ability to leave a lasting creative mark on a high-growth tech company. You’ll join a marketing leadership team committed to creative excellence and long-term brand building, in an environment where high standards, originality, and bold ideas are valued and expected.&lt;/p&gt;
