&lt;p&gt;We are seeking our first Director of Finance &amp;amp; Billing Operations to join Rockbot, bringing a passion for operational excellence, systems design, and scalable revenue infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Rockbot continues transforming how revenue flows through the business with Salesforce, MuleSoft, and Ironclad, this role will play a critical role in connecting the dots behind the scenes. You’ll help translate contracts, orders, and customer activity into accurate billing, collections, and revenue reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who is a natural builder, enjoys solving complex operational challenges, and takes pride in creating scalable systems that make life easier for both customers and internal teams. You’ll inherit a billing environment supporting more than 12,000 customers across SaaS subscriptions, usage-based services, enterprise contracts, hardware, professional services, and advertising products. You’ll have the opportunity to bring structure, automation, and operational excellence to a function undergoing meaningful transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
