&lt;li&gt;Manage billing operations for SaaS subscriptions, usage-based services, enterprise contracts, hardware, professional services, and advertising products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish scalable billing policies, controls, workflows, and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive collections performance, cash flow optimization, and DSO improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Accounting on month-end close, reconciliations, revenue reporting, and audit support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage Avalara sales tax compliance and exemption processing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own billing support operations, identify recurring issues, and drive long-term process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design and Improve Quote-to-Cash Processes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Sales, RevOps, Finance, GTM Systems, and Engineering to refine billing processes as upstream systems mature.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define billing triggers, operational handoffs, and data requirements that support accurate invoicing and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and resolve data quality issues that create downstream billing and collections challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve workflows supporting complex customer structures, including enterprise, government, education, multi-location, and franchise-style accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously evaluate opportunities to improve automation, scalability, and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
